{"tid":249970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[統計] 連登有幾多人平時係活躍於社交網絡？","createTime":"2017-05-19T16:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T23:19:31.000Z","uid":68589,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f777a75f4d48ba5334c8a96b27e02460dbad6f1a","tid":249970,"uid":68589,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:54:03.000Z","msg":"活躍：正評<br />\n唔活躍：負評<br />\n<br />\n個人認為「活躍」既定義：<br />\n一﹑平均一個星期最少post一次貼身既野（生活相／一d諗法／身邊發生既事）<br />\n二﹑多like (&gt;10)，d post間中都會有互動comment<br />\n三﹑「社交網絡」例子：fb﹑ig<br />\n<br />\n點解你係「活躍」/「唔活躍」？<br />\n你點睇活躍同唔活躍既人？"},{"pid":"40c8418ee0aa5f6a9bb98018553ebdd4cb2e18a8","tid":249970,"uid":104664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:33:47.000Z","msg":"日日有po ig 不過無連電話同面書 一直都0 follower<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係純粹自言自語 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191ee1c203982393289dc1d916c56cc18efdd4bf","tid":249970,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日有po ig 不過無連電話同面書 一直都0 follower<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係純粹自言自語 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b2330a0678007073f10b7ceb3e7cc022fce45c","tid":249970,"uid":15335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T23:19:31.000Z","msg":"唔活躍， 一日都係開一次睇下頭幾個post就算<br />\n不過post相都定會多過10個like嘅<br />\n對於活躍嘅人我其實無咩感覺，佢哋鐘意點咪點囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}